askg-data:Paper-170201105v2-Section-1-Paragraph-14 a askg-onto:Paragraph ;
    rdfs:label "Paragraph 4"@en ;
    domo:Text "Figure 1: Joint 2D-3D-Semantic data. We present a dataset that provides a variety of mutually registered modalities including: RGB images, depth, surface normals, global XYZ images as well as instance-level semantic annotations in 2D and 3D. The modalities are in 2D (*e.g*. RGB images), 2.5D (*e.g*. depth) and 3D (*e.g*. meshes)."@en ;
    askg-onto:hasSentence askg-data:Paper-170201105v2-Section-1-Paragraph-14-Sentence-141,
        askg-data:Paper-170201105v2-Section-1-Paragraph-14-Sentence-142,
        askg-data:Paper-170201105v2-Section-1-Paragraph-14-Sentence-143,
        askg-data:Paper-170201105v2-Section-1-Paragraph-14-Sentence-144,
