    rdfs:label "Sentence 2"@en ;
    domo:Text "We hope the dataset fuels development of cross and joint modality techniques as well as unsupervised approaches leveraging the regularities in large-scale manmade spaces."@en ;
    askg-onto:index "2"^^xsd:int .

