    rdfs:label "Sentence 1"@en ;
    domo:Text "Over the past few years, advances in the field of 3D imaging have led to manufacturing inexpensive sensors and mainstreaming their use in consumer products (*e.g*."@en ;
    askg-onto:index "1"^^xsd:int .

