    rdfs:label "Paragraph 1"@en ;
    domo:Text "We collected the data using the Matterport Camera [\\[2\\]](#page-7-16), which combines 3 structured-light sensors to capture 18 RGB and depth images during a 360◦ rotation at each"@en ;
