askg-data:Paper-170201105v2-Section-6-Paragraph-64 a askg-onto:Paragraph ;
    rdfs:label "Paragraph 4"@en ;
    domo:Text "scan location. The output is the reconstructed 3D textured meshes of the scanned area, the raw RGB-D images, and camera metadata. We used this data as a basis to generate additional RGB-D data and make point clouds by sampling the meshes. We semantically annotated the data directly on the 3D point cloud, rather than images, and then projected the per point labels on the 3D mesh and the image domains."@en ;
